quran[49]{c,v,t}:
  43,57,"Tuma nde geЙ—al neene Maryama on piyiranoo misal, tawaa yoo, yimЙ“e maa Й“en no sooЖҙira Й—um"
  43,58,"Й“e wi'i: \"Ko reweteeЙ—i amen Й—in Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude, kaa ko kanko?\" ЖҒe piyiranaali ma ngal (misal), si wanaa fii wennjugol. Wurin, ko Й“e yimЙ“e saЙ—tuЙ“e wennje"
  43,59,"Awa (Iisaa) wonaali, si wanaa jeyaaЙ—o mo Men neemini e mun, Men waЙ—i mo misal woannde Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en"
  43,60,"Si Men haajuno, Men waЙ—titirayno on Malaa'ika, ko lomtoo ka leydi"
  43,61,"Pellet non, ko o anndinorde Darngal. Wata on sikkito fii maggal. Jokkee lam, ko Й—um woni laawol focciingol ngol"
  43,62,"Wata seytaane falo on ! tawde pellet, ko o gaГұo mon Й“annguЙ—o"
  43,63,"Nde Iisaa ardunoo e Й“annguЙ—i Й—in, o maaki: \"GomЙ—ii mi ardanii on e ГұeeГұal, e no mi Й“annginirana on yoga e ko luutondirЙ—on e muuЙ—um. Haray hulee Allah, Й—oftoЙ—on mi"
  43,64,"Pellet, ko Alla Woni Joomi am e Joomi mon. Rewee Mo. Ko Й—um woni laawol focciingol ngol"
  43,65,"Feddeeji Й—in luutondiri hakkunde majji. Bone woodanii Й“en yedduЙ“e, immorde e lepte Гұalaande muusuЙ—e"
  43,66,"Hara Й“e habbi si wanaa nde Darngal ngal ardata Й“e e juhal, hara Й“e so'aa anndude"
  43,67,"WelduЙ“e Й“en, nden Гұalnde, yoga maЙ“Й“e ko ayrooЙ“e yoga; si wanaa gomЙ—umЙ“e Й“en"
  43,68,Ko onon yo jeyaaЙ“e Am ! Kulol alanaa on hannde; wonaa on sunotooЙ“e kadi
  43,69,"Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й“e woni jebbiliiЙ“e"
  43,70,"naatee ka Aljanna, onon e nannduЙ“e e mon, hiЙ—on saЙ—nee"
  43,71,"[GollooЙ“e] hino wanngindinee e maЙ“Й“e, mirannji kaЕӢЕӢe e ГұedduЙ—e; hino ton kadi: kala ko wonkii muuyetee, gite dakmitoo. Hara le, ko on duumotooЙ“e ton"
  43,72,"Ko on woni Aljanna mo roniniraЙ—on, sabu kon ko gollaynoЙ—on"
  43,73,"Hino woodani on ton, muuyanteeЙ—i Й—uuЙ—uЙ—i, Й—i Гұaamoton e mun"
  43,74,"Pellet, bomЙ“e Й“en, ko ka lepte Jahannama Й“e luttoyta"
  43,75,"Й“e hoynantaake, tee hara ko Й“e taЖҙiiЙ“e ton"
  43,76,"Men tooГұaani Й“e few, si ko woni, ko kamЙ“e woni tooГұuЙ“e Й“en"
  43,77,"ЖҒe nodda: \"Ko an yo Maaliku ! Yo Joomi maa gaynu fii amen !\" O wi'i: \"Pellet, ko on luttooЙ“e [ton]"
  43,78,"GomЙ—ii Men addanii on goonga kan ; kono Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e e mon, ko aГұuЙ“e goonga"
  43,79,Kaa Й“e eЙ“Й“u feere ? Doo ko Men fewjooЙ“e
  43,80,Maa hara Й“e sikku Men nanataa gunndooji maЙ“Й“e e sirru maЙ“Й“e? OoвҖҷowoye! NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“en hino maandina takko maЙ“Й“e
  43,81,"Maaku: \"Si Hinaranko On no jogitii Й“iЙ—Й—o, ko min adotonoo rewude on"
  43,82,"Senayee woodanii JeyЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, JeyЙ—o Arsi kin; laaЙ“uЙ—o e kon ko Й“e sifrotta Mo. @Corrected"
  43,83,"AccuЙ“e Й“e jumpa, Й“e fija haa Й“e hawroya e Гұalaande maЙ“Й“e ndeЙ“e fodaa"
  43,84,"Ko Kanko woni On reweteeЙ—o ka kammu e reweteeЙ—o ka leydi, ko Kanko kadi woni Г‘eeГұo, AnnduЙ—o On"
  43,85,"Barke heewanii On Mo woodani Й—um, laamu kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde majji. Ko ka Makko anndal fii Darngal woni. Ko ka Makko kadi rutteteЙ—on"
  43,86,"ЖҠi Й“e rewata Й—in gaanin Makko jeyah tefoore, si wanaa seediiЙ“e goonga Й“en, hara hiЙ“e anndi"
  43,87,"Ko pellet, si a lamndike Й“e, ko hommbo woni ko tagi Й“e? ЖҒe wi'ay: \"Ko Allah\". Ko honno non Й“e yiiliraa"
  43,88,"[Himo anndi kadi] fii ko (NulaaЙ—o) on maakunoo kon: \"Ko an yo Joomi, pellet, Й“ee ko yimЙ“e Й“e gomЙ—intaa"
  43,89,"Awa yaafo Й“e, maakaa: \"Kisal !\" Aray ndebe annda"
  44,1,"Haa, Miim"
  44,2,Mi woondirii Defere Й“anngunde nden
  44,3,"Men jippinirii nde e jemma barkinaaЙ—o, Men siforii wonde jertinooЙ“e"
  44,4,Ko e on (jemma) woni ko senndetee kala fiyaaku ГұeГұaaЙ—o
  44,5,ЖҠum ko yamiroore immorde ka Amen. Men siforii wonde NulooЙ“e
  44,6,"yurmeende immornde ka Joomi maa. Pellet, ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, AnnduЙ—o On"
  44,7,"JeyЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, si wonii ko on yananaaЙ“e"
  44,8,"ReweteeЙ—o goo alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Himo wuurna, Himo wara. JeyЙ—o on Jeyi baabiraaЙ“e mon aramЙ“e Й“en"
  44,9,"Ko woni tun, Й“e wonii e sikke, hiЙ“e fija"
  44,10,Habbito Гұalnde kammu ngun ardata e curki feeГұuuki
  44,11,"suddayki yimЙ“e Й“en. [ЖҒe wi'anee]: \"ЖҠum ko lepte muusuЙ—e"
  44,12,"Joomi amen, huncan men lepte Й—en. Menen ko men gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  44,13,"Ko honno Й“e waajitorta, ko goongo NulaaЙ—o Й“annginЙ—o ariino Й“e"
  44,14,"Refti Й“e hucciti, Й“e wi'i: \"Ko tinndinaaЙ—o, haangaaЙ—o"
  44,15,"Awa ko Men ittooЙ“e lepte Й—en seeЙ—a; kono pellet, ko on ruttitotooЙ“e"
  44,16,"Г‘alnde Men nanngiroyta wippannde mawnde nden, pellet, ko Men yottoytooЙ“e"